# Demo videos. Recommended formats:
#   demo.mp4   — primary 60-90s walkthrough (drag-and-drop into GitHub README;
#                or commit if <100MB)
#   battle.gif — quick loop of Meme Battle voting (3-5s, animated GIF)
#
# GitHub tip: edit the README on github.com → drag any .mp4 file into the
# editor. GitHub hosts it at user-images.githubusercontent.com and inserts
# the URL. Replace the placeholder in README.md with that URL.
